data.description: Lovely home with loads of character eagerly awaiting the next chapter nestled in fabulous Lake Wales!  This home features a decorative deck on the front of the house, perfect for sipping morning coffee and enjoying the sunshine.  Enter through the front door into a living room with lots of natural light and a bonus room just beyond.  The open kitchen has a sink that overlooks the back yard and a small half bath plus laundry room.  The 2 bedrooms are separated by a full bathroom and both have wonderful windows for light.  With a partially fenced yard and TONS of potential, this wonderful home has it all!  Possibility for a fantastic rental property close to shopping and dining!  Call today for your private showing of this lovely slice of Florida paradise!
